<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/140738-i-just-reread-mission-song-after-a-number">I just reread Mission Song after a number of years and immediately had memory of having watched it on screen. It was not made into a movie that I can find, so does anyone know if it was adapted by BBC, perhaps, in a series they produced on intelligence? This is driving me batty but I am very certain I watched it besides having read it. Thanks for any help here.</a>
</div>
