<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1824297-i-wondered-did-anyone-have-a-problem-with">I wondered: Did anyone have a problem with Bruno Salvo being, well, for lack of a better term, somewhat of a traitor? I mean Mr. Anderson told him up front that this mission was secretive and he&#39;d have to get down and dirty. Salvo agreed wholeheartedly to dive in with both hands and do his best. Was it really his call to determine these were the bad guys, steal from his employers. take their bonus $ and rat them out</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1824297'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F18988.The_Mission_Song">like</a></span>

</li>
