              <span id="reviewTextContainer1509537658" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2931977422467659272">Is says something when I can only get halfway through a book by one of my favour authors and have to give up. It looked to have all the makings of a good story with good characters until it became too tedious, bogged down in a complex lecture on the problems of Africa. I found myself skipping boring pages and then stopped. </span>

          </span>
